      <title>亚洲股市跟随美国科技股下跌、日元上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者开始退出今年推动牛市的人工智能狂热，亚洲股市下跌。在下周日本央行会议召开之前，日元连续第四天上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 22:35:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国经济低迷导致美欧石油在亚洲价格昂贵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/china-s-gloomy-economy-makes-us-european-oil-too-pricey-in-asia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国经济低迷导致美国和欧洲的石油在亚洲的竞争力下降，亚洲的炼油商更倾向于选择距离本土较近的石油供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/china-s-gloomy-economy-makes-us-european-oil-too-pricey-in-asia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 13:04:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>GE Vernova 计划在事故发生后对风力发电机叶片进行大规模检查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/ge-vernova-identified-manufacturing-deviation-at-blade-factory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[通用电气 Vernova 公司 (GE Vernova Inc.) 计划对公司生产的每一片海上风力涡轮机叶片进行重新检查，因为该公司发现，供应美国在建项目中最近发生断裂的零部件的工厂存在“材料偏差”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/ge-vernova-identified-manufacturing-deviation-at-blade-factory</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 11:50:52 GMT</pubDate>
